### Sample Product API Tests

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Create a Sample Product - Protein Supplements
POST {{baseUrl}}/sample-products
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Protein Supplements",
  "description": "Nutritional supplements for muscle building and recovery",
  "code": "PROT_SUPP"
}

### 2. Create a Sample Product - Pulses & Lentils
POST {{baseUrl}}/sample-products
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
