### 5. Get all Sample Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/sample-products
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 6. Get all Sample Products (including inactive)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sample-products?includeInactive=true
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 7. Get a specific Sample Product by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/sample-products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 8. Update a Sample Product
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/sample-products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated description for protein supplements product",
  "isActive": true
}

### 9. Soft delete a Sample Product (deactivate)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/sample-products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 10. Hard delete a Sample Product (permanent)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/sample-products/{{productId}}/hard
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}